      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Sports Gaming Opportunity Act of 2017</b></p> <p> This bill amends the federal judicial code to exempt a lottery, sweepstakes, or other betting, gambling, or wagering scheme authorized by a state by a statute enacted on or after January 1, 2017, and in effect not later than January 1, 2021, from the prohibition against a governmental entity, or a person acting pursuant to the law or compact of<em><strong> </strong></em>a governmental entity, sponsoring, operating, advertising, or promoting sports gambling.</p>]]></text>
